    "glossary_filter_tier3": "Lim phau ntawv qhia lus mus qhia only Tier 3 cov lus—domain-tshwj xeeb technical lo lus (e.g., photosynthesis, democracy, denominator). These lo lus yog: essential rau understanding tshwj xeeb cov ntsiab, typically defined hauv textbooks, thiab limited hauv siv outside subject thaj av. Tier 3 lo lus should be taught hauv conntawv nyeem during cov ntsiab cov lus qhia. They yog important rau unit tab sis tsawg transferable than Tier 2 lo lus. Lim here mus pom which technical lo lus require explicit lub ntsiab before tub ntxhais kawm tuaj yeem kev nkag cov ntsiab. Provide kev pom kev txhawb thiab ntau exposures rau retention.",
