    "tool_fullpack": "One-nyem comprehensive kev pab cuam tiam. Creates ua kom tiav zaj lus qhia package suav nrog: AI-analyzed cov ntsiab cov ntsiab lus, multi-theem simplified cov ntawv (3 reading theem), kev pom cov lus phau ntawv qhia lus nrog duab, kev sim nrog lo lus teb key, zaj lus qhia kev npaj aligned mus tus qauv, graphic organizer/outline, sau ntawv scaffolds, thiab timeline (yog tias chronological cov ntsiab). Perfect rau: ceev zaj lus qhia prep, substitute xib fwb packets, niam txiv communication cov khoom siv, thiab IEP documentation. txhua feem yog separately editable after tiam. Xa tawm entire pack as PDF bundle los yog sib koom via link. Khawss 20-30 minutes compared mus tab tom tsim txhua kev pab cuam individually.",
