    "venn_sorted_item": "yam koj muaj already placed hauv pawg zone. Nyem mus xaiv it thiab reveal tshais kev xaiv, los yog rub mus reposition. While kev kawm, feel free mus tshais yam nyob nruab nrab zones as koj understanding develops. checkmark tshwm rau saum correctly placed yam after checking. Incorrectly placed yam tuaj yeem be moved mus retry. tswv yim: place yam koj yog confident txog thawj, then siv those decisions mus inform uncertain placements. txhua yam contributes mus koj overall qhov tseeb qhab nia. Completely sorted duab piav qhia nrog siab qhov tseeb earn bonus XP.",
    "venn_bank_item": "yam waiting mus be hoob kawmified. Located hauv holding bank below Venn duab piav qhia. Rub mus appropriate zone: Teeb (left voj voog), Teeb B (sab xis voj voog), los yog Shared (overlapping center). Rau keyboard users: nyem mus xaiv, then siv zone pob nias mus place. Bank yam represent lub tswv yim qhov ntawd need categorization. tag nrho yam must be placed mus ua kom tiav activity. yam tuaj yeem be returned mus bank yog tias reconsidering. cov lus qhia: Nyeem pawg labels carefully before placing yam, thiab consider dab tsi makes yam similar los yog different.",
