    "header_cloud_sync": "Control ua nws tus kheej cloud backup ntawm koj work. thaum enabled (recommended): koj cov ntsiab, kev teeb tsa, thiab kev nce qib sync automatically mus cloud. Benefits: kev nkag work los ntawm any device, ua nws tus kheej backup prevents cov ncauj lus loss, lub sij hawm tiag sync nrog tub ntxhais kawm during kev sib ntsib. thaum disabled: work khaws locally only—faster rau unstable connections tab sis no backup. Hloov qhia sync status: spinning = actively syncing, check = tau khaws, kev ceeb toom = sync kev yuam kev. Re-qhib thaum koj muaj stable internet mus xa mus accumulated kev hloov. Cloud sync requires internet connection tab sis siv minimal bandwidth. tag nrho cov ncauj lus yog encrypted hauv transit thiab at rest via Firebase security.",
