    "bot_mic_btn": "Activate speech-mus-cov ntawv kev nkag rau talking mus AlloBot. Nyem mus pib speaking—koj lo lus tshwm sim as cov ntawv hauv kev sib tham. Requires microphone permission. Benefits: hands-free interaction, faster than typing, natural conversation flow, thiab kev nkag mus tau rau tub ntxhais kawm nrog motor difficulties. suab kev nkag auto-submits after pause detection los yog nyem Xa. Ua hauj lwm alongside typed kev nkag—xaiv preferred method anytime. Best hauv quiet environments rau qhov tseeb. Noise tuaj yeem cause transcription kev yuam kev—hais clearly thiab at homrate pace. hom lus detection matches koj interface hom lus kev teeb tsa.",
    "tool_math": "Tsim tus qauv-aligned lej cov teeb meem nrog scaffolded solutions. cov yam ntxwv: kev pom representations (tus lej kab, thaj av homls, graph), cov theem-by-cov theem worked piv txwv nrog xib fwb notes, real-world lo lus cov teeb meem themed mus koj cov ntsiab, differentiated kev nyuaj theem, thiab lo lus teb keys qhov ntawd tuaj yeem be hidden rau kev ntsuam xyuas. kev txhawb conceptual understanding by qhia WHY txhua cov theem ua hauj lwm, tsis just yuav ua li cas. Cov teeb meem automatically incorporate cov lus los ntawm koj qhov chaw cov ntawv rau cross-curricular connections. Xa tawm as printable worksheets los yog mus sib tham digital xyaum.",
