    "tool_simplified": "Transform qhov chaw cov ntawv rau pom tau version at ntau reading theem (grades 1-12+). cov yam ntxwv suav nrog: ua nws tus kheej Lexile/qib-theem adjustment, cov lus simplification nrog hover lub ntsiab, kab lus shortening rau sib tw readers, thiab tsis yog yuav tsum ob hom lus kev tawm. kev txhawb UDL Principle 1 (Ntau Means ntawm Representation) by providing tib yam cov ntsiab at different kev nyuaj theem. Siv Sib piv hom mus qhia thawj thiab simplified side-by-side. Perfect rau differentiated cov lus qhia, ELL scaffolding, thiab IEP accommodations. AI maintains key lub tswv yim while adjusting hom lus kev nyuaj.",
    "word_sounds_review_start": "Pib mus sib tham phonics activity siv koj prepared lo lus daim ntawv teev npe. Before starting, kev tshuaj xyuas: lo lus yog hauv intended order, phonemes yog correctly segmented, duab represent lub tswv yim well, thiab activity type yog tau xaiv. Once started: tub ntxhais kawm work dhau los ntawm lo lus sequentially (los yog xib fwb controls pace), txhua lo lus presents tau xaiv activity type (Break It Down, Rhyme Time, los yog Tracing), kev nce qib autosaves, thiab XP yog awarded rau mastery. Pib thaum koj chav kawm yog ready— thawj lo lus tshwm immediately. koj tuaj yeem pause thiab resume anytime without losing kev nce qib.",
