    "word_sounds_review_regen_word": "Tsim replacement lo lus los ntawm tib yam phoneme family los yog pawg. Siv thaum: lo lus yog too yooj yim los yog too nyuaj rau koj tub ntxhais kawm, AI-tau tsim lo lus yog problematic, los yog koj want ntau variety. replacement matches koj thawj criteria (syllable suav, phoneme pattern). tshiab lo lus muaj: fresh phoneme segmentation, tshiab AI duab, thiab suab. Thawj lo lus yog removed thiab cannot be recovered—regeneration yog permanent. yog tias koj want mus keep ob qho, ntxiv tshiab lo lus instead. cov lus qhia: Pkev tshuaj xyuas replacement before deciding yog tias it fits koj zaj lus qhia zoo dua than thawj.",
    "word_sounds_review_move_word": "Rub qhov no lo lus mus tshiab qhov chaw hauv activity sequence. Reordering kev pabs: tsim los ntawm yooj yim mus nyuaj, pawg thematic lo lus together, sequence by phoneme kev nyuaj, los yog match koj zaj lus qhia flow. Rub thiab tso los yog siv arrow pob nias rau kev nkag mus tau. Sequence order affects: yuav ua li cas tub ntxhais kawm kev nce qib dhau los ntawm activity, pacing ntawm kev nyuaj, thiab zaj dab neeg flow rau dab neeg-connected lo lus. Consider ordering by: syllable suav (1-syllable thawj), phoneme type (luv vowels before ntev), los yog frequency (feem ntau lo lus before rare). ua nws tus kheej ordering kev xaiv muaj hauv kev teeb tsa. cov lus qhia: Pkev tshuaj xyuas full sequence before starting mus ensure logical progression.",
    "word_sounds_review_delete_word": "Permanently tshem qhov no lo lus los ntawm current lo lus Word Sounds kev sib ntsib. Siv thaum: lo lus does tsis fit zaj lus qhia objectives, lo lus yog inappropriate rau tub ntxhais kawm population, los yog koj want shorter activity. Deletion yog immediate thiab cannot be undone—yog tias koj might want lo lus later, consider moving it mus end instead. Minimum lo lus suav yog 3 rau valid activity. Deleting below minimum yuav prompt koj mus ntxiv ntau lo lus before starting. lo lus suav adjusts automatically after deletion. cov lus qhia: Lwv after kev tshuaj xyuasing tag nrho lo lus tab sis before starting activity nrog tub ntxhais kawm.",
    "word_sounds_review_play_word": "Pkev tshuaj xyuas yuav ua li cas qhov no lo lus yuav be pronounced during activity. suab siv koj current suab kev teeb tsa (suab selection, ceev, volume). Mloog mus: verify pronunciation yog correct rau koj dialect, assess yog tias ceev yog appropriate rau koj tub ntxhais kawm, thiab xyaum koj own pronunciation before leading cov lus qhia. Nyem ntau times mus repeat. suab yog tib yam as tub ntxhais kawm yuav hear during activities thiab rau saum flashcard. yog tias pronunciation seems wrong, check yog tias lo lus has ntau pronunciations (nyeem vs. nyeem) thiab consider adding phonetic cov lus qhia hauv lo lus spelling.",
    "word_sounds_review_play_phonemes": "Hear txhua tus kheej sound hauv lo lus spoken separately, then blended. Rau lo lus CAT: koj hear /k/... /æ/... /t/... then cat. Qhov no demonstrates phoneme segmentation (breaking lo lus rau cov suab) thiab blending (combining cov suab rau lo lus)—two foundational kev txawj rau reading. ceev adjusts automatically rau learner theem. Tsim phonemic awareness, single strongest predictor ntawm early reading kev kov yeej. Siv rau: phonics cov lus qhia, phonological awareness intervention, thiab kev pabing sib tw readers connect letters mus cov suab. Research qhia explicit phoneme cov lus qhia improves decoding kev txawj.",
    "word_sounds_review_image_gen": "Tsim kev pom representation ntawm qhov no cov lus lo lus siv AI duab tiam. duab kev txhawb cov lus acquisition by connecting lo lus mus concrete kev pom (dual coding theory). Rau abstract lo lus, AI tsim metaphorical los yog contextual duab. Art hom follows koj current duab hom kev teeb tsa. duab tshwm sim hauv lo lus Word Sounds activities, flashcard, thiab printable cov khoom siv. Regenerate yog tias duab does tsis clearly represent lub tswv yim los yog koj want variety. cov lus qhia: Siv consistent art hom within zaj lus qhia rau kev pom coherence. duab tuaj yeem be downloaded rau siv hauv lwm cov khoom siv.",
    "word_sounds_review_phoneme_bank": "Kev nkag ua kom tiav phoneme library containing tag nrho English speech cov suab. Siv thaum: lo lus contains sound tsis automatically recognized, koj want mus ntxiv regional pronunciations, los yog koj yog teaching phonemes explicitly. library muaj: consonants (stops, fricatives, affricates), vowels (luv, ntev, r-controlled, diphthongs), thiab blends. txhua phoneme has: IPA symbol, suab sample, thiab piv txwv lo lus. Ntxiv phonemes mus koj lo lus los yog tsim kev nyiam phoneme sequences. Essential rau explicit phonics cov lus qhia thiab accommodating dialect variations.",
    "word_sounds_review_distractor_input": "Hloov raws siab nyiam lo lus teb kev xaiv rau rhyming activities. Rau Rhyme Time: sau correct rhyming lo lus thiab distractor kev xaiv qhov ntawd do tsis rhyme. Distractors should be: phonetically similar tab sis tsis true rhymes (tsim productive kev sib tw), age-appropriate cov lus, thiab distinct enough mus avoid confusion txog correct lo lus teb. zoo distractors kev xeem whether tub ntxhais kawm nkag siab rhyming cov qauv versus surface similarity. koj tuaj yeem regenerate AI-suggested distractors los yog tsim koj own. cov lus qhia: Siv distractors qhov ntawd sib koom consonants tab sis differ hauv vowels mus specifically lub hom phiaj rhyme discrimination kev txawj.",
    "word_sounds_review_play_distractor": "Hear yuav ua li cas qhov no distractor lo lus cov suab before siv it hauv activity. suab pkev tshuaj xyuas kev pabs verify: pronunciation yog clear, lo lus yog distinguishable los ntawm lub hom phiaj, thiab suab quality yog acceptable. Siv mus check qhov ntawd tub ntxhais kawm yuav be able mus hear difference nyob nruab nrab correct rhymes thiab distractors. yog tias pronunciation yog unclear los yog too similar mus lub hom phiaj, consider choosing different distractor. suab siv koj current suab kev teeb tsa. Pkev tshuaj xyuas tag nrho distractors mus ensure activity suab yog consistent thiab clear rau koj tub ntxhais kawm.",
