    "bingo_speed_slider": "Control yuav ua li cas quickly Bingo Caller advances mus tom ntej clue during auto-ua si. Range: maj mam (20 vib nas—gives time mus nrhiav thiab think), Medium (12 vib nas—qhib tab sis comfortable), ceev (6 vib nas—challenging, kev tshuaj xyuas pace). ceev affects: time nyob nruab nrab clues, reading pace ntawm lub ntsiab, thiab overall kev ua si duration. Rau thawj-time tus ua si los yog nyuaj cov lus, siv maj mam. Rau familiar lo lus los yog energetic kev tshuaj xyuas, siv ceev. siv tes hom ignores qhov no kev teeb tsa—koj control timing nrog tom ntej pob nias. Kho mid-kev ua si yog tias tub ntxhais kawm need ntau los yog tsawg time.",
