    "source_upload_btn": "Coj los cov ntsiab los ntawm cov ntaub ntawv rau saum koj device. Supported hom: PDF (cov ntawv extracted automatically, duab analyzed via OCR), duab (JPG, PNG—cov ntawv extracted via AI vision), lo lus cov ntawv (DOCX), Plain cov ntawv (TXT), thiab PowerPoint (PPTX—speaker notes extracted). Large cov ntaub ntawv yog processed hauv chunks. Rau PDFs nrog nyuaj formatting, cov ntawv extraction preserves structure. Rau handwritten notes los yog worksheets, AI vision interprets cov ntsiab. Maximum cov ntaub ntawv size: 25MB. cov ntaub ntawv yog processed locally thiab tsis stored—only extracted cov ntawv yog tau siv. cov lus qhia: Rau best cov txiaj ntsig nrog duab, ensure zoo lighting thiab clear cov ntawv.",
    "source_link_btn": "Coj los cov ntsiab directly los ntawm web pages. Muab tso any URL mus rho tawm: main article cov ntawv (ads thiab navigation removed), duab nrog captions, thiab embedded media descriptions. Ua hauj lwm nrog: news articles, Wikipedia, educational sites, blog posts, thiab most public web pages. AI intelligently identifies main cov ntsiab thaj av, ignoring sidebars thiab footers. Rau paywalled cov ntsiab, only freely pom tau cov ntawv yog extracted. YouTube URLs rho tawm duab yeeb yaj kiab transcripts thaum muaj. Imported cov ntsiab becomes koj qhov chaw material rau tag nrho tiam cov cuab yeej. cov lus qhia: Verify extracted cov ntsiab matches thawj—layout differences may affect extraction.",
