    "persona_panel": "Engage hauv AI-powered conversations nrog historical figures, scientists, authors, los yog fictional tus cwj pwm. tub ntxhais kawm ask lo lus nug thiab txais responses hauv-tus cwj pwm raws rau saum accurate historical/literary knowledge. cov yam ntxwv: Socratic hom (tus cwj pwm asks probing lo lus nug rov qab), kev xav cov lus qhia after conversation, XP nqi zog rau quality lo lus nug, thiab conversation transcripts rau kev ntsuam xyuas. kev txhawb perspective-taking, primary qhov chaw analysis, thiab engagement nrog cov ntsiab. xib fwb tuaj yeem hloov raws siab nyiam tus cwj pwm knowledge thiab speaking hom. Zoo rau: history (interview Lincoln), science (talk mus Marie Curie), literature (kev sib tham nrog Atticus Finch).",
    "persona_card": "Tus kheej tus cwj pwm daim npav rau selection. daim npav qhia: tus cwj pwm name, portrait, luv description, thiab expertise tags. Nyem mus xaiv rau conversation. Ntau selections (2-4): enables phab ntsa discussion hom qhov twg tus cwj pwm interact thiab debate. Selection kev xaiv suav nrog: Historical Figures (scientists, leaders, artists), Literary tus cwj pwm (los ntawm books, plays, myths), Subject Experts (kev nyiam personas rau domain knowledge), thiab Custom (tsim koj own). Selected tus cwj pwm yog highlighted. Deselect by nyeming again. phab ntsa discussions tsim dynamic multi-perspective conversations zoo rau exploring controversy thiab ntau viewpoints. cov lus qhia: Xaiv tus cwj pwm nrog different perspectives rau txaus siab debates.",
    "concept_sort_panel": "Tsim categorization activities qhov twg tub ntxhais kawm muab cais yam rau pawgs. Tsim conceptual understanding by requiring tub ntxhais kawm mus txheeb xyuas attributes thiab relationships. cov yam ntxwv: kev nyiam pawg (2-4 pawgs), rub-thiab-tso los yog keyboard-pom tau sorting, immediate kev tawm tswv yim nrog explanations, undo/redo rau exploration, thiab analytics qhia feem ntau misconceptions. kev txhawb science (living vs. non-living), hom lus arts (parts ntawm speech), lej (odd vs. even), thiab any hoob kawmification task. AI automatically tsim quality distractors. Xa tawm as printable cut-thiab-muab cais los yog digital mus sib tham.",
