    "math_quantity": "Configure yuav ua li cas many lej cov teeb meem mus tsim. Range 1-10 cov teeb meem per tiam. Fewer cov teeb meem (1-3): ceev xyaum, warm-up activities, exit tickets. Homrate (4-6): tus qauv xyaum teeb, homework assignment. ntau cov teeb meem (7-10): comprehensive xyaum, kev ntsuam xyuas preparation. txhua problem muaj: problem statement, work space, thiab lo lus teb key. AI varies tus lej thiab contexts across cov teeb meem while maintaining consistent kev nyuaj thiab lub tswv yim focus. Tiam time increases slightly nrog suav. Cov teeb meem tuaj yeem be regenerated individually yog tias needed. cov lus qhia: Pib nrog fewer cov teeb meem mus check appropriateness, then tsim ntau once satisfied nrog kev nyuaj theem.",
    "math_context": "Connect lej cov teeb meem mus koj qhov chaw cov ntsiab ntsiab lus. thaum enabled: problem scenarios qhov xa mus koj qhov chaw material (yog tias kev kawm txog ecosystems, cov teeb meem involve animal populations). thaum disabled: cov teeb meem siv generic contexts (shopping, sports, qhov yooj yim scenarios). Contextual cov teeb meem: increase engagement, reinforce cov ntsiab kev kawm, thiab demonstrate real-world lej application. Ua hauj lwm best thaum qhov chaw cov ntsiab has countable elements. Abstract cov ntsiab may tsim tsawg natural connections. AI adapts contexts naturally while maintaining mathematical validity. Conntawv nyeem does tsis hloov lej kev txawj kev xyaumd, only presentation. cov lus qhia: Qhib rau cross-curricular integration, kaw thaum pure lej xyaum yog lub hom phiaj.",
    "quiz_reflection_count": "Ntxiv qhib-response lo lus nug qhov ntawd require written explanations, tsis just lo lus teb selection. These lo lus nug: assess deeper understanding beyond recognition memory, tsim metacognitive kev txawj (explain koj thinking), provide insight rau tub ntxhais kawm reasoning, thiab prepare tub ntxhais kawm rau extended sau ntawv tasks. txhua kev xav lo lus nug muaj rubric-aligned prompt. AI tsim lo lus nug qhov ntawd connect mus qhov chaw cov ntsiab thiab kev kawm objectives. Rau formative kev ntsuam xyuas, 1-2 kev xav lo lus nug provide valuable insight. Rau summative, 2-3 tsim balanced kev ntsuam xyuas ntawm ob qho knowledge thiab application.",
    "quiz_dok": "Teeb cognitive kev nyuaj ntawm tau tsim lo lus nug siv Webb tob ntawm Knowledge framework. DOK 1 (Recall): qhov yooj yim facts, lub ntsiab, yooj yim procedures—Who, dab tsi, thaum. DOK 2 (kev txawj/Lub tswv yim): Sib piv, hoob kawmify, explain cause-effect—requires qee mental processing. DOK 3 (Strategic Thinking): Tshuaj xyuas, evaluate, kos conclusions—requires reasoning thiab pov thawj. DOK 4 (Extended Thinking): Design, synthesize, apply across contexts—nyuaj real-world application. Higher DOK requires ntau critical thinking. Match DOK mus koj kev kawm objectives: DOK 1-2 rau cov lus/kev nkag siab checks, DOK 3-4 rau deeper kev ntsuam xyuas. Mixing theem tsim balanced kev ntsuam xyuas.",
    "quiz_custom_instructions": "Provide kev nyiam guidance mus duab AI kev sim tiam. piv txwv: Focus rau saum cov lus thiab lub ntsiab, Suav nrog kev pom interpretation lo lus nug, Avoid lo lus nug txog third nqe lus, Tsim lo lus nug qhov ntawd require comparing lub tswv yim, Suav nrog fill-hauv--blank along nrog ntau kev xaiv, thiab Ua lo lus nug appropriate rau ELL tub ntxhais kawm. AI follows koj cov lus qhia thaum selecting cov ntsiab, crafting lo lus nug, thiab determining kev nyuaj. Siv rau: curriculum kev sib raug, kev ntsuam xyuas customization, differentiation, thiab avoiding sensitive cov ntsiab. cov lus qhia tuaj yeem qhov xa mus tshwj xeeb parts ntawm koj qhov chaw cov ntawv. Clear, tshwj xeeb cov lus qhia tsim zoo dua cov txiaj ntsig than vague guidance.",
    "lesson_plan_custom_additions": "Hloov raws siab nyiam zaj lus qhia kev npaj tiam nrog tshwj xeeb requirements. piv txwv: Suav nrog bell-ringer activity, Ntxiv SEL check-hauv moment, Siv 5E homl structure, Suav nrog station rotation, Ntxiv technology integration tshooj, thiab Suav nrog niam txiv communication note. AI incorporates koj additions rau tau tsim zaj lus qhia structure. Requirements tuaj yeem hais kom meej: additional tshooj (warmup, closure), tshwj xeeb tswv yim (think-pair-sib koom, jigsaw), time allocations (15-min direct cov lus qhia max), thiab hom elements (lub rooj rau differentiation, checklist rau cov khoom siv). Ntau additions tuaj yeem be combined. Clear cov lus qhia tsim zoo dua cov txiaj ntsig. cov lus qhia: Suav nrog koj must-muaj elements qhov ntawd AI might tsis suav nrog by default.",
