    "chat_framework_select": "Xaiv tus qauv framework rau curriculum kev sib raug cov yam ntxwv. muaj frameworks suav nrog: Feem ntau Core State tus qauv (ELA/Lej), tom ntej Tiam Science tus qauv (NGSS), State-tshwj xeeb tus qauv (qhov twg muaj), thiab International Baccalaureate (IB). Selection affects: tus qauv nrhiav cov txiaj ntsig, kev sib raug suggestions, thiab objective recommendations. Framework determines which tus qauv tshwm sim hauv consult reports. tuaj yeem be changed anytime—tsis locked. Most xib fwb siv their state/district yuav tsum tau framework. Ntau frameworks tuaj yeem be referenced across different cov ntsiab thaj av. cov lus qhia: Teeb koj primary framework once hauv kev teeb tsa mus avoid selecting txhua time.",
    "chat_grade_select": "Teeb theem qib kawm lim rau tus qauv thiab cov ntsiab. Selection affects: which tus qauv yog shown, reading theem recommendations, thiab age-appropriate suggestions. qib bands muaj: Pre-K, K-2, 3-5, 6-8, 9-12, thiab Higher Ed. tus qauv consultation filters mus tau xaiv qib. cov ntsiab recommendations align nrog qib expectations. tuaj yeem be changed per query—tsis locked globally. Multi-qib hoob kawmrooms tuaj yeem kho per activity. theem qib kawm also influences: cov lus kev nyuaj, kab lus structure, thiab lub tswv yim scaffolding hauv AI suggestions. cov lus qhia: Teeb accurately mus get most relevant tus qauv thiab suggestions rau koj tub ntxhais kawm.",
