    "chat_autofill": "ua nws tus kheej configuration assistance los ntawm AI analysis. thaum enabled: AlloBot reads koj qhov chaw cov ntsiab, extracts key cov ncauj lus (cov ncauj lus, cov lus, ntsiab lus, approximate theem qib kawm), thiab pre-fills cov cuab yeej kev teeb tsa. Benefits: faster setup, consistent kev sib raug, thiab reduced siv tes configuration. Pre-filled kev teeb tsa tuaj yeem be adjusted before tiam. Autofill examines: cov lus kev nyuaj, subject matter, cov ntawv structure, thiab cov ntsiab ntsiab lus. Ua hauj lwm best nrog: well-structured qhov chaw cov ntawv, clear educational cov ntsiab, thiab sufficient cov ntsiab ntev. Kaw only yog tias: koj prefer full siv tes control los yog autofill suggestions yog consistently wrong. cov lus qhia: Leave enabled rau efficiency—koj tuaj yeem always override tus kheej kev teeb tsa.",
    "analysis_generate_button": "Khiav AI analysis rau saum koj qhov chaw cov ntsiab. Tiam time depends rau saum tob kev teeb tsa. kev tawm muaj: readability statistics, main idea cov ntsiab lus, key cov lus nrog lub ntsiab, ntsiab lus identification, cov ntawv structure analysis, potential tub ntxhais kawm misconceptions, discussion lo lus nug, thiab teaching opportunity highlights. cov txiaj ntsig tshwm sim hauv organized tsab ntawv ceeb toom hom. Analysis informs: which cov cuab yeej mus tsim tom ntej, yuav ua li cas mus differentiate, thiab dab tsi mus pre-teach. Xa tawm analysis rau zaj lus qhia planning documentation. Analysis reveals dab tsi might be challenging rau tub ntxhais kawm before they encounter it. Siv insights mus anticipate lo lus nug thiab prepare kev txhawb.",
    "outline_generate_button": "Tsim organized representation ntawm koj cov ntsiab. kev tawm kev xaiv suav nrog: Traditional Outline (hierarchical nrog Roman numerals), Lub tswv yim Map (kev pom connections nyob nruab nrab ideas), Bullet Cov ntsiab lus (streamlined key lub tshoj), thiab Cornell Notes Template (pre-structured nrog cue kem). hom selection tshwm before tiam. AI identifies: main ideas, supporting kev meej, relationships, thiab key cov lus. Outlines tuaj yeem be: filled hauv by AI (ua kom tiav) los yog left as templates (tub ntxhais kawm ua kom tiav). Mus sib tham version allow expanding/collapsing tshooj. Xa tawm rau handouts los yog digital distribution. Zoo rau: pre-reading overview, study guides, thiab note-taking scaffolds.",
    "dashboard_import_btn": "Nqa los tub ntxhais kawm records los ntawm spreadsheet cov ntaub ntawv. CSV hom must suav nrog: tub ntxhais kawm identifier (name los yog codename hauv kem ). tsis yog yuav tsum kem: pawg assignment, preset accommodations, prior qhab nia, thiab kev nyiam fields. Template muaj rau rub los qhia expected hom. Coj los merges nrog existing cov ncauj lus los yog replaces raws rau saum koj selection. Siv rau: starting tshiab semester nrog rosters, syncing los ntawm SIS xa tawm, los yog restoring los ntawm backup. Imported tub ntxhais kawm tshwm sim hauv roster ready rau pawg assignment. Large imports may take moment. Validate coj los cov txiaj ntsig before relying rau saum cov ncauj lus. cov lus qhia: Xa tawm koj roster thawj mus pom expected hom.",
    "dashboard_export_csv": "Rub los ua kom tiav analytics cov ncauj lus as spreadsheet. Xa tawm muaj: tub ntxhais kawm identifiers, pawg assignments, activity kev ua tiav records, kev sim qhab nia by lo lus nug, time rau saum task, XP totals, flag history, thiab kev sib ntsib timestamps. CSV qhib hauv Excel, Google Sheets, los yog any spreadsheet program. Siv rau: gradebook integration (theej qhab nia), cov ncauj lus analysis (lim thiab muab cais), archival (semester backups), thiab reporting (pivot lub rooj). kem yog clearly labeled rau yooj yim interpretation. Large chav kawm may tsim substantial cov ntaub ntawv. Xa tawm regularly rau cov ncauj lus safety. cov lus qhia: Tsim semester folder thiab xa tawm after txhua major kev ntsuam xyuas rau longitudinal kev tshawb.",
    "dashboard_clear_btn": "Permanently lwv tag nrho tub ntxhais kawm records los ntawm dashboard. Qhov no action yog irreversible. tag nrho cov ncauj lus yog removed: rosters, qhab nia, activity logs, flags, thiab analytics. Requires confirmation before executing. Siv nrog extreme caution only thaum: starting completely fresh nrog tshiab tub ntxhais kawm, testing thiab need mus pib dua, los yog privacy requirements mandate cov ncauj lus deletion. Consider exporting before clearing as backup. After clearing, dashboard yog empty until tshiab tub ntxhais kawm join los yog yog imported. Historical cov ncauj lus cannot be recovered. cov lus qhia: End ntawm year clearing should follow district cov ncauj lus retention policies.",
    "dashboard_stat_students": "Suav ntawm unique tub ntxhais kawm who muaj connected mus koj kev sib ntsib. muaj: tub ntxhais kawm currently online, previously connected tub ntxhais kawm, thiab imported roster entries. tus lej updates hauv lub sij hawm tiag as tub ntxhais kawm join. Nyem tus lej mus pom breakdown: currently qhib (green), connected today (blue), kaw 7+ days (gray). Useful rau: kev tshawb participation tshaj time, identifying attendance cov qauv, thiab verifying roster completeness. Does tsis suav nrog tub ntxhais kawm who never connected their codename. yog tias tus lej seems wrong: check rau duplicate codenames, verify imports, los yog kev tshuaj xyuas pawg assignments. Siab variation nyob nruab nrab kev sib ntsib may indicate kev nkag los yog engagement issues.",
    "dashboard_stat_quiz": "chav kawm-wide kev sim qhab nia average as feem pua. Calculated los ntawm: tag nrho completed kev sim hauv current kev sib ntsib los yog date range. Nyem mus pom breakdown: distribution chart (yuav ua li cas many tub ntxhais kawm at txhua qhab nia range), lo lus nug-by-lo lus nug performance (which yam were hardest), thiab trend tshaj time. Average updates hauv lub sij hawm tiag during ncaj qha kev sib ntsib. Consider: averages tuaj yeem zais wide variation, so kev tshuaj xyuas distribution. Industry guidelines: 80%+ suggests appropriate kev nyuaj, 60-79% indicates challenging cov ntsiab, below 60% may need prerequisite kev tshuaj xyuas. Siv qhov no metric mus: kho pacing, txheeb xyuas re-teaching needs, thiab validate kev ntsuam xyuas kev nyuaj.",
    "dashboard_stat_flags": "Suav ntawm tub ntxhais kawm nrog concerns requiring xib fwb kev tshuaj xyuas. Flags yog raised rau: low kev sim qhab nia (below threshold), concerning cov ntsiab hauv responses (safety lim triggers), extended inactivity during kev sib ntsib, repeated incorrect lo lus teb (possible frustration), thiab xib fwb-marked issues. Nyem tus lej mus pom flagged tub ntxhais kawm daim ntawv teev npe nrog flag reasons. Flags do tsis automatically notify niam txiv—xib fwb kev tshuaj xyuass thawj. Clear flags after addressing concerns. Siab flag counts may indicate: cov ntsiab kev nyuaj, engagement issues, los yog kev sib ntsib cov teeb meem. Siv flags mus prioritize which tub ntxhais kawm need immediate check-hauv during los yog after kev sib ntsib.",
    "dashboard_stat_activities": "Aggregate suav ntawm completed kev kawm activities. muaj: phau ntawv qhia lus kev tshuaj xyuass, kev sim attempts, kev mus ncig tshooj, sorting kev ua si, thiab tag nrho mus sib tham cov yam ntxwv. Higher tus lej indicate engagement. Nyem mus pom breakdown by: activity type (which activities yog most tau siv), tub ntxhais kawm (who yog most/least qhib), thiab time (activity trends). Sib piv mus tub ntxhais kawm suav rau per-tub ntxhais kawm average. Low totals may indicate: kev sib ntsib issues, unclear cov lus qhia, los yog engagement cov teeb meem. Kev ua tiav counts toward XP, so tub ntxhais kawm yog incentivized mus ua kom tiav activities. Activities yog marked ua kom tiav thaum submission los yog kev kov yeej criteria yog met, tsis just thaum tau qhib.",
