    "dashboard_detail_safety": "Kev nkag safety monitoring cov ncauj lus rau tus kheej tub ntxhais kawm. Shows: any cov ntsiab flagged by AI safety filters, flag pawg (concerning hom lus, emotional distress indicators, off-cov ncauj lus cov ntsiab, potential bullying references), timestamps, thiab conntawv nyeem around flagged cov ntsiab. AI flags yog sensitive thiab may tshaj-trigger—xib fwb judgment determines appropriate response. False positives yog feem ntau; genuine concerns yog rare tab sis important. Siv qhov no phab ntsa mus: nkag siab tub ntxhais kawm emotional state, txheeb xyuas potential issues early, thiab cov ntawv concerns yog tias escalation yog needed. tag nrho flags yog confidential thiab pom tau only mus verified xib fwb.",
