    "adventure_low_quality": "Hloov duab quality rau kev mus ncig kev pom. Low quality: faster tiam (2-3 vib nas vs 8-10), lower API costs, smaller cov ntaub ntawv sizes, thiab adequate rau most chav kawm siv. Siab quality: ntau meej duab, zoo dua rau printing, thiab showcase quality. Quality affects: resolution, kev meej theem, thiab artistic refinement. Low quality yog often sufficient rau instructional purposes. Siab quality yog zoo dua rau: yam ntxwvd projects, printed cov khoom siv, thiab kev pom portfolios. kev teeb tsa applies mus tshiab generations only, existing duab unchanged. cov lus qhia: Siv low quality during zaj lus qhia development, hloov mus siab rau final version.",
