    "concept_sort_card_item": "Mus sib tham sorting daim npav. Primary interaction: rub thiab tso mus pawg bins above. Alternative: siv arrow pob nias rau keyboard-pom tau sorting (Tab mus xaiv, arrows mus tshais). Touch devices: tap thiab hold mus rub. Double-nyem (los yog press Sau twice) mus kho yam cov ntawv hauv xib fwb hom. daim npav qhia: lub tswv yim cov ntawv, tsis yog yuav tsum duab, thiab pawg xim once placed. daim npav hauv wrong pawg tuaj yeem be moved again before checking. Rub rov qab mus deck mus tshem los ntawm pawg. Smooth animations qhia movement. cov lus qhia: yog tias rub-thiab-tso yog difficult, siv keyboard navigation los yog kev nkag mus tau kev teeb tsa rau alternative kev nkag methods.",
