    "fullpack_generate": "One-nyem comprehensive kev pab cuam tiam. Creates: Adapted cov ntawv (ntau reading theem), kev sim (MCQ thiab kev xav), phau ntawv qhia lus (kev pom cov lus nrog suab), zaj lus qhia kev npaj (structured cov lus qhia), thiab Discussion lo lus nug (Socratic cov lus qhia). tag nrho kev pab cuam yog interconnected thiab aligned. Takes 60-90 vib nas mus tsim full bundle. Perfect rau: ceev zaj lus qhia prep, substitute xib fwb kev pab cuam, thiab comprehensive unit cov khoom siv. txhua feem tuaj yeem be edited independently after tiam. kev pab cuam khaws together as project. Zoo rau xib fwb nrog limited planning time. cov lus qhia: Review thiab hloov raws siab nyiam tus kheej feem before chav kawm siv.",
    "chat_voice_mode": "Transform AI Guide rau suab conversation assistant. thaum enabled: hais koj lo lus nug siv microphone kev nkag (no typing needed), hear AI responses spoken aloud, thiab enjoy natural rov qab-thiab-forth dialogue. Perfect rau: hands-free interaction while working rau saum projects, tub ntxhais kawm who struggle nrog typing, auditory cov tub ntxhais kawm, thiab kev nkag mus tau needs. suab hom siv koj tau xaiv TTS suab thiab ceev. Microphone activates thaum koj nyem los yog tuaj yeem be teeb mus always-mloog. Mus interrupt ntev responses, nyem Nres los yog pib speaking. Zoo rau one-rau saum-one tutoring conversations nrog AlloBot.",
    "chat_auto_send": "Control suab kev nkag kev coj noj coj ua. thaum ON (Auto-xa): cov xov sends after 1-2 vib nas ntawm silence, enables hands-free conversation, thiab flows naturally like talking. thaum OFF (siv tes): koj kev tshuaj xyuas transcription before sending, tuaj yeem kho mistakes, thiab muaj ntau control. Auto-xa yog faster tab sis may misinterpret pauses. siv tes yog slower tab sis ntau accurate. Rau ceev lo lus nug, auto-xa ua hauj lwm well. Rau nyuaj lo lus nug los yog thaum qhov tseeb matters, siv siv tes. Silence detection adjusts mus ambient noise. cov lus qhia: Siv siv tes hom thaum thawj starting mus pom transcription qhov tseeb, hloov mus auto thaum comfortable.",
    "chat_save": "Preserve kev sib tham conversation rau future kev nkag. Khawsd conversations suav nrog: tag nrho cov xov (yours thiab AI), timestamps, thiab any tau tsim cov ntsiab. Kev nkag tau khaws chats los ntawm History phab ntsa. Siv rau: revisiting kev pabful explanations, sharing tutoring kev sib ntsib nrog xib fwb, thiab kev tshawb kev kawm kev nce qib. Conversations tuaj yeem be: exported as cov ntawv, shared via link, thiab printed rau records. Khawsd chats do tsis expire during koj subscription. tub ntxhais kawm tuaj yeem khaws chats as portfolio pov thawj. xib fwb tuaj yeem kev tshuaj xyuas tau khaws chats mus nkag siab tub ntxhais kawm lo lus nug. cov lus qhia: Khaws particularly kev pabful explanations mus qhov xa mus later.",
    "chat_show_me": "Qhib mus sib tham cov yam ntxwv discovery. Ask lo lus nug like qhov twg yog phau ntawv qhia lus? los yog yuav ua li cas do I hloov font? thiab AI yuav: highlight relevant UI element nrog kev pom spotlight, provide cov theem-by-cov theem cov lus qhia, thiab offer mus navigate koj there. Perfect rau: tshiab users kev kawm interface, finding hidden cov yam ntxwv, thiab reducing training time. AI understands synonyms—saying cov lus instead ntawm phau ntawv qhia lus still ua hauj lwm. yog tias cov yam ntxwv requires tshwj xeeb conditions (e.g., cov ntsiab must be tau tsim thawj), AI explains prerequisites. Reduces frustration thiab kev txhawb tus kheej-directed kev kawm ntawm cov cuab yeej.",
    "chat_expand": "Resize kev sib tham interface. Expanded: full-screen kev sib tham, maximum conversation space, focused interaction. Compact: sidebar phab ntsa, pom lwm cov ntsiab while chatting, multitasking friendly. Hloov nrog qhov no pob nias los yog keyboard shortcut. Expanded yog zoo dua rau: extended conversations, reading ntev responses, thiab focused tutoring. Compact yog zoo dua rau: ceev lo lus nug while working, qhov xa mus while tab tom tsim, thiab limited screen space. kev sib tham remains qhib hauv ob qho views. Switching preserves conversation. cov lus qhia: Siv expanded rau kev kawm conversations, compact rau ceev lookups.",
