    "dashboard_detail_games": "Comprehensive kev ua si performance cov ntsiab lus rau tau xaiv tub ntxhais kawm. Displays cov txiaj ntsig across tag nrho cov lus thiab cov ntsiab kev ua si suav nrog: Memory Match, lo lus-lub ntsiab Matching, Syntax Scramble, Crossword, Timeline, Lub tswv yim Muab cais, Venn duab piav qhia, Bingo, thiab lo lus Scramble. Rau txhua kev ua si played, qhia: tus lej ntawm plays, qhov tseeb/qhab nia, thiab performance trends. Siv qhov no cov ncauj lus mus txheeb xyuas which kev ua si-raws kev kawm activities yog most effective rau txhua tub ntxhais kawm thiab qhov twg additional xyaum may be needed.",
