    "dashboard_detail_word_sounds": "lo lus Word Sounds performance cov ncauj lus rau tau xaiv tub ntxhais kawm. Shows metrics los ntawm lo lus Word Sounds Studio phonics activities suav nrog: qhov tseeb feem pua, kev sib ntsib qhab nia, lo lus kev xyaumd, thiab activity kev ua tiav kev meej. cov ncauj lus comes los ntawm Break It Down (phoneme segmentation), Rhyme Time (rhyming identification), thiab Letter Tracing activities. Siv qhov no mus track phonemic awareness development thiab txheeb xyuas tshwj xeeb phonics kev txawj qhov ntawd need additional xyaum. pom tau only thaum tub ntxhais kawm has completed lo lus Word Sounds activities.",
    "dashboard_live_sync": "Connect mus ncaj qha chav kawm kev sib ntsib mus monitor tub ntxhais kawm kev nce qib hauv real time. Nyem mus sau kev sib ntsib code — tub ntxhais kawm hauv qhov ntawd kev sib ntsib yuav tshwm sim hauv koj dashboard nrog ncaj qha-updating cov ncauj lus (📡 lub cim). koj tuaj yeem pom their activity kev ua tiav, kev sim qhab nia, XP, fluency history, kev ua si performance, thiab safety flag summaries as they work. Nyem again while connected mus disconnect. Ncaj qha sync siv Firestore thiab requires internet connectivity. kev sib ntsib codes yog tau tsim thaum tub ntxhais kawm join kev sib ntsib. cov ncauj lus flows one-way los ntawm tub ntxhais kawm mus xib fwb rau privacy compliance. Only muaj hauv district-hosted deployments (tsis Canvas).",
    "dashboard_rti_monitor": "Tus kheej tub ntxhais kawm RTI kev nce qib monitoring phab ntsa qhia meej intervention cov ncauj lus. Displays: current tier assignment nrog xim-coded lub cim (Tier 1/2/3), hoob kawmification reasoning, tshwj xeeb performance metrics (kev sim qhab nia, fluency, activity kev ua tiav), sparkline trend chart rau fluency thiab kev ua si qhab nia tshaj time, thiab actionable recommendations. xib fwb tuaj yeem siv Configure pob nias mus kho tier thresholds. Qhov no cov ncauj lus kev txhawb IEP documentation thiab cov ncauj lus-driven instructional decisions. Metrics hloov tshiab thaum tshiab tub ntxhais kawm cov ncauj lus yog imported los yog synced ncaj qha.",
    "dashboard_rti_summary": "chav kawm-theem RTI (Response mus Intervention) overview qhia distribution ntawm tub ntxhais kawm across intervention tiers. Displays: Tier 1 (green, rau saum track), Tier 2 (yellow, needs monitoring), thiab Tier 3 (red, intensive kev txhawb needed) counts nrog kev pom lub cim. txhua tier qhia tub ntxhais kawm suav thiab feem pua. cov ntsiab lus also muaj donut-hom visualization ntawm tier distribution. Siv qhov no mus quickly txheeb xyuas yuav ua li cas many tub ntxhais kawm need additional kev txhawb thiab mus track chav kawm-wide trends tshaj time. Tier assignments yog calculated automatically los ntawm kev sim qhab nia, kev ua si performance, activity kev ua tiav, thiab fluency cov ncauj lus.",
    "dashboard_safety_toggle": "Hloov visibility ntawm safety flag cov ncauj lus hauv xib fwb dashboard. thaum ON (default): Safety Flags kem tshwm hauv tub ntxhais kawm lub rooj qhia flag counts thiab critical alerts (🚨). thaum OFF: kem yog hidden rau cleaner saib. Important: qhov no hloov only controls tso tawm — safety flags yog ALWAYS collected silently hauv background regardless ntawm qhov no kev teeb tsa. AI-powered safety checks khiav rau saum every tub ntxhais kawm cov xov hauv Socratic kev sib tham, Persona Interviews, thiab Kev mus ncig hom. Hloov state yog tau khaws mus localStorage thiab persists across kev sib ntsib. Siv qhov no mus reduce kev pom clutter thaum safety monitoring yog tsis koj current focus.",
    "roster_manage_button": "Qhib tub ntxhais kawm roster management phab ntsa. Roster phab ntsa lets xib fwb: saib tag nrho tub ntxhais kawm hauv current kev sib ntsib, manage tub ntxhais kawm nicknames thiab kev teeb tsa, assign differentiated kev pab cuam mus tshwj xeeb tub ntxhais kawm los yog pawgs, configure pawg-tshwj xeeb kev teeb tsa (reading theem, kev pom density, TTS ceev, hom lus), thiab tsim tub ntxhais kawm pawgs rau targeted cov lus qhia. roster yog populated los ntawm kev sib ntsib joins thiab tuaj yeem be manually edited.",
