    "adventure_consistent_characters": "Consistent tus cwj pwm cov yam ntxwv: thaum enabled, AI yuav attempt mus maintain tib yam kev pom appearance rau tus cwj pwm across tag nrho qhov chaw hauv koj kev mus ncig. Qhov no means hero, companions, thiab recurring tus cwj pwm yuav look tib yam hauv every illustration, tab tom tsim kev pom continuity. Qhov no siv qhov xa mus-raws duab tiam — thawj qhov chaw establishes txhua tus cwj pwm's look, thiab subsequent qhov chaw sim mus match it. Zoo rau zaj dab neeg kev nkag siab thiab tus cwj pwm kev tshawb.",
