    "persona_panel": "Lub panel sib tham AI Persona - koom nrog cov kev sib tham tseeb nrog cov neeg keeb kwm, cov kws tshawb fawb, cov cwj pwm hauv ntawv, los yog cov personas custom. Siv AI siab dua los ua piv txwv cov qauv hais lus, kev paub, thiab kev xav uas raws lub sij hawm. Zoo rau kev tsom xam cov hauv paus tseeb, kev saib ntawm lwm tus, thiab cov kev xyaum tsim kev khuv leej. Txhawb ntau hom kev teb: In-Character (raws nraim), Educational (nrog cov scaffolds kawm), los yog Mixed (sib npaug).",
    "persona_card": "AI persona ready rau conversation. txhua daim npav qhia tus cwj pwm's name, time period, thiab expertise thaj av. Nyem mus pib interview - AI yuav respond authentically raws rau saum their historical context, beliefs, thiab knowledge. Siv personas rau primary qhov chaw analysis, perspective-taking exercises, los yog creative sau ntawv inspiration.",
