    "persona_select_button": "Xaiv qhov no persona mus begin koj interview los yog conversation. Once tau xaiv, koj'll sau kiv ntsuab kev sib tham interface qhov twg koj tuaj yeem ask lo lus nug, nrhiav xyuas their perspective, thiab earn XP rau meaningful exchanges. AI responds raws rau saum tus cwj pwm's historical knowledge, personality, thiab cultural context.",
