    "persona_custom_instructions": "Ntxiv tshwj xeeb requirements rau yuav ua li cas persona should behave during conversations. piv txwv: focus rau saum tshwj xeeb time period, emphasize certain beliefs los yog tus nqi, maintain particular speech cov qauv, los yog limit responses mus historically accurate knowledge. xib fwb tuaj yeem siv qhov no mus align personas nrog tshwj xeeb kev kawm objectives.",
    "persona_response_mode": "Xaiv yuav ua li cas persona responds mus tsim different kev kawm kev paub. IN tus cwj pwm: Fully kiv ntsuab historical suab nrog no homrn explanations. EDUCATIONAL: tus cwj pwm speaks tab sis muaj kev kawm scaffolds, cov lus kev txhawb, thiab context. MIXED: Balanced approach nrog authentic suab plus occasional clarifications. Xaiv raws rau saum tub ntxhais kawm readiness thiab kev kawm lub hom phiaj.",
    "persona_free_response": "Type koj own qhib-ended response instead ntawm selecting los ntawm pre-written kev xaiv. Free response hom promotes creative expression, critical thinking, thiab authentic dialogue kev txawj. Responses yog analyzed rau historical qhov tseeb, empathy, thiab tob ntawm inquiry. Higher-quality lo lus nug earn ntau XP.",
    "persona_hints_toggle": "Qhia los yog zais response suggestions thiab conversation cov lus qhia. thaum enabled, system provides scaffolded lo lus nug starters, historical conntawv nyeem cov lus qhia, thiab engagement suggestions. Kev pabful rau tub ntxhais kawm tshiab mus historical inquiry los yog those needing kev txhawb nrog qhib-ended lus nuging. xib fwb tuaj yeem kaw cov lus qhia rau ntau qib siab kev ntsuam xyuas scenarios.",
    "persona_show_hints": "Tso tawm kev pabful cov lus qhia rau txaus siab nrog persona. cov lus qhia suav nrog historically relevant lo lus nug mus ask, topics tus cwj pwm would find interesting, thiab cov lus qhia qhov ntawd lead mus deeper understanding. Zoo rau tub ntxhais kawm who need scaffolding los yog aren't sure yuav ua li cas mus begin historical interview.",
    "persona_submit_btn": "Xa koj cov xov mus persona tus cwj pwm. koj lo lus nug los yog response yog analyzed rau relevance thiab tob. AI persona yuav respond authentically raws rau saum their historical context, knowledge, thiab personality. Well-crafted lo lus nug qhov ntawd qhia historical understanding earn bonus XP.",
