      "iep_goal_bank_fraction_specific": "🎯 IEP lub hom phiaj bank — tshwj xeeb rau feem",
      "pre_formatted_smart_goals_for_iep_team": "Cov SMART hom phiaj uas teeb tseg rau IEP pab pawg. Txhua lub hom phiaj txuas rau ib qho CCSS standard, qhia cov qhov chaw ntaub ntawv soj ntsuam kev vam meej hauv AlloFlow, thiab teev cov kev pab nquag. Luam thiab hloov rau koj tus tub ntxhais kawm.",
