      "lesson_plan_templates": "📚 Cov qauv phiaj xwm qhia",
      "ready_to_use_micro_units_3_5_days_each": "Cov micro-unit npaj siv (3-5 hnub rau ib qho) rau cov ntsiab feem nquag. Txhua phiaj xwm txuas cov haujlwm rau cov tab Fraction Lab tshwj xeeb kom koj demo lossis muab haujlwm ncaj qha.",
      "where_do_fractions_come_from": "Cov feem los ntawm qhov twg?",
      "the_earliest_fraction_notation_dates_t": "Cov cim feem thawj tshaj nyob rau Egypt qub kwvyees 1800 BCE. Cov neeg Egypt siv «unit fraction» — cov feem uas muaj tus lej saum yog 1 xwb (xws li 1/2, 1/3, 1/4). Lawv sau lwm cov feem ua cov unit fraction sib ntxiv: 2/5 = 1/3 + 1/15. Cov cim kab niaj hnub no (tus lej saum saum tus lej hauv) los ntawm cov neeg Arab kws lej thaum nrab caij kwvyees xyoo 1200 CE.",
      "where_do_the_fraction_words_come_from": "Cov lus feem los ntawm qhov twg?",
      "numerator_comes_from_the_latin_numerar": "«Numerator» (tus lej saum) los ntawm Latin «numerare» (suav) — nws suav muaj pes tsawg feem. «Denominator» (tus lej hauv) los ntawm «denominare» (tis npe) — nws tis npe qhov loj ntawm cov feem. Ua ke: tus lej hauv tis npe hom daim; tus lej saum suav koj muaj pes tsawg daim ntawd.",
      "the_decimal_point": "Lub decimal point",
      "decimals_as_we_know_them_were_populari": "Cov decimal li peb paub raug ua kom nrov los ntawm Simon Stevin xyoo 1585 hauv nws phau ntawv «De Thiende» (Ib Feem Kaum). Ua ntej ntawd, feem yog tib txoj kev qhia cov lej uas tsis yog lej tag. Lub decimal point raug lees txais thoob ntiaj teb thaum xyoo 1700 xwb.",
      "what_does_percent_mean": "Feem pua txhais li cas?",
      "percent_comes_from_the_latin_per_centu": "«Percent» (feem pua) los ntawm Latin «per centum» — «rau ib puas». Yog li 25% txhais tias 25 rau 100, lossis 25/100. Lub cim % tau hloov los ntawm lo lus luv «per c.» hauv Italian kev lag luam sau xyoo pua 15.",
      "what_is_a_reciprocal": "Reciprocal yog dab tsi?",
      "the_reciprocal_of_a_b_is_b_a_flip_it_u": "Tus reciprocal ntawm a/b yog b/a — ntxeev nws. Txhua feem uas tsis yog xoom muaj ib tus reciprocal. Qhov sib npaug ntawm ib feem thiab nws tus reciprocal yeej ib txwm yog 1: (3/4) × (4/3) = 12/12 = 1. Qhov no yog vim li cas kev faib nrog ib feem zoo ib yam li kev sib npaug nrog nws tus reciprocal.",
      "why_is_1_2_the_most_used_fraction": "Vim li cas 1/2 yog feem uas siv ntau tshaj?",
      "1_2_is_the_most_common_fraction_in_eve": "1/2 yog feem nquag tshaj hauv kev hais lus niaj hnub vim nws nyob raug hauv nruab nrab ntawm 0 thiab 1. Nws kuj yog tib feem uas peb ib txwm hais ua lo lus: «ib nrab» tsis yog «ib rau ob». Lwm cov lus kuj muaj cov lus tshwj xeeb rau 1/3 thiab 1/4 thiab (ib feem peb, ib feem plaub).",
      "pizza_is_mathematical": "Pizza yog lej",
      "a_pizza_is_a_perfect_fraction_model_be": "Pizza yog ib qauv feem zoo tshaj vim nws yog ib lub voj voog (yog li txhua daim tawm ntawm qhov chaw nruab nrab), cov daim yooj yim suav, thiab qauv haum rau lej cov ntsiab lus: ib feem n/d yog n cov feem sib luag ntawm tag nrho d cov feem sib luag.",
      "when_fractions_are_not_enough": "Thaum cov feem tsis txaus",
      "some_numbers_like_and_2_cannot_be_writ": "Ib txhia lej, xws li π thiab √2, tsis tuaj yeem sau ua ib feem ntawm ob tus lej tag. Cov no hu ua cov lej irrational. Cov Pythagorean (kwvyees 500 BCE) hais tias tua tus kws lej Hippasus thaum nws ua pov thawj tias √2 tsis tuaj yeem sau ua ib feem.",
      "continued_fractions": "Cov continued fraction",
      "any_real_number_can_be_written_as_a_co": "Txhua tus lej tiag tuaj yeem sau ua ib «continued fraction» — ib feem uas nyob hauv xws li 1 + 1/(2 + 1/(2 + 1/(2 + ...))). Qhov no muab qhov kwvyees feem zoo tshaj. π ≈ 22/7 los ntawm ob peb lub sib thawj; zoo dua yog 355/113.",
      "fractions_in_music": "Cov feem hauv suab paj nruag",
      "musical_pitch_ratios_are_fractions_the": "Cov ratio suab paj nruag yog cov feem. Octave yog ratio 2:1 (frequency ob npaug). Perfect fifth yog 3:2. Major third yog 5:4. Pythagoras pom tias cov ratio lej tag yooj yim tsim cov suab sib haum.",
