      "bird_flight_costs_12x_their_resting_me": "Kev ya ntawm noog raug nqi kwv yees 12x ntawm lawv qhov resting metabolic rate (Kleiber txoj cai). Roj muab 9 kcal ib gram — cov fuel muaj zog nteev tshaj plaws hauv biology. Ua ntej tsiv, cov noog nkag mus rau ib qho ",
