      "altitude_physiology": "✈️ Altitude physiology",
      "some_birds_migrate_at_extreme_altitude": "Qee cov noog tsiv ntawm qhov siab heev — Bar-headed Geese hla Himalayas ntawm 29,000 ft. Rub tus slider los saib seb cov xwm txheej hloov li cas.",
      "air_density": "Air density",
      "wind": "Cua",
      "extreme_altitude": "Qhov siab heev! ",
      "bar_headed_geese_survive_here_thanks_t": "Bar-headed Geese ciaj sia ntawm no ua tsaug rau hemoglobin uas khi oxygen ruaj dua, ntsws loj dua, thiab mitochondria uas ua tau zoo dua. Feem ntau cov tsiaj mammal yuav tsaus muag ntawm qhov siab no. Lawv cov ntshav muaj ib qho hemoglobin mutation tshwj xeeb (Pro→Ala ntawm qhov chaw 119) uas ntxiv oxygen affinity 50%.",
      "high_altitude_zone": "High altitude zone. ",
      "many_songbirds_migrate_at_this_range_w": "Ntau cov noog hu nkauj tsiv ntawm qhov range no, qhov chaw uas cov cua nyias txo drag tab sis oxygen tsawg. Cov noog them rov qab nrog kev ua pa uas zoo dua: lawv lub airflow system ib txoj kev rho oxygen ob leeg thaum ua pa nkag thiab tawm, tsis zoo li cov mammal ntsws uas rho tsuas yog thaum ua pa nkag.",
      "common_cruising_altitude": "Cruising altitude ib txwm. ",
      "most_migrants_fly_between_5_000_15_000": "Feem ntau cov migrant ya nruab nrab 5,000 thiab 15,000 ft. Cov kub ntawm cua poob kwv yees 3.5 °F txhua 1,000 ft (standard temperature gradient). Cov noog xaiv qhov siab los nrhiav cov cua zoo — tib tug noog yuav ya ntawm 2,000 ft ib hmos thiab 12,000 hmo tom ntej.",
      "low_altitude": "Low altitude. ",
      "hummingbirds_and_some_shorebirds_fly_c": "Hummingbirds thiab qee cov shorebird ya ze rau saum npoo, tshwj xeeb tshaj yog saum dej. Kev ya qis muaj kev nyab xeeb dua ntawm kev khov, tab sis txhais tau tias air resistance ntau dua thiab cua txhawb tsawv tsawg dua. Thaum lub sijhawm hla Gulf of Mexico 600 mais, feem ntau cov noog ya nruab nrab 1,000 thiab 3,000 ft.",
