      "wind_science_for_migrators": "🌬️ Wind science rau cov migrant",
      "thermals": "Thermals",
      "thermals_are_columns_of_rising_warm_ai": "Thermals yog cov kem ntawm cov cua sov sawv uas tsim thaum lub hnub ua kom av kub tsis sib npaug. Cov npoo tsaus (chaw nres tsheb, teb laij) tsim cov thermal muaj zog dua cov npoo pom kev (dej, hav zoov). Cov noog soaring xws li dav thiab dav dawb soar hauv spiral rau hauv cov thermal, tau qhov siab yam tsis ntxais tis. Ces lawv glide mus rau lub thermal tom ntej, tsim ib txoj «thermal highway» uas cawm zog, ib txoj kev freeway saum ntuj.",
      "orographic_lift": "Orographic lift",
      "when_wind_encounters_a_mountain_it_is_": "Thaum cua ntsib ib lub roob, nws raug thawb mus saum toj raws li sab windward. Qhov no tsim ib txoj kab cua sawv uas cov noog ridge-soaring (xws li golden eagle) siv. Ntawm sab leeward, cua nqis sai, tsim ib thaj «rotor» txaus ntshai ntawm cov cua turbulent uas nqis. Yog li ntawd cov noog thiab cov pilot zam sab leeward ntawm cov roob.",
      "sea_breezes": "Sea breezes",
      "land_heats_faster_than_water_during_th": "Av kub sai dua dej thaum nruab hnub. Cua sov sawv saum av thiab cua txias dua ntws los ntawm hiav txwv los hloov nws, tsim ib «sea breeze» mus rau ntug hiav txwv. Thaum hmo ntuj txoj kev sib txawv. Cov noog migratory siv cov cua ntug hiav txwv predictable no los txuag zog. Thaj convergence, qhov chaw uas sea breeze ntsib cov cua inland, feem ntau tsim cov thermal uas cov noog siv los tau qhov siab.",
      "jet_streams": "Jet streams",
      "high_altitude_jet_streams_are_narrow_b": "High-altitude jet streams yog cov band nqaim ntawm cua ceev heev (100-200 mph) ntawm 30,000-40,000 ft. Txawm hais tias feem ntau cov noog ya qis dua cov jet stream ntau, qee cov migrant xws li Bar-tailed Godwit nce saum 20,000 ft los ntes cov cua qhov siab zoo. Cov os raug ntes los ntawm radar ntawm 29,000 ft saum Himalayas, qhov chaw uas oxygen tsawg thiab qhov kub poob mus rau -50 °F.",
      "wind_shear": "Wind shear",
      "wind_shear_is_a_sudden_change_in_wind_": "Wind shear yog ib qho hloov tam sim ntawm ceev los yog kev taw cua thoob ib qho kev deb luv. Nws txaus ntshai rau cov noog thiab cov dav hlau ob leeg. Cov microburst (cov kem cua nqis tam sim) thaum lub sijhawm cua daj cua dub tsim wind shear hnyav ze av. Cov noog hnov cov hloov ntawm siab thiab feem ntau ncua kev tsiv thaum cov storm front tuaj ze.",
      "beaufort_scale": "Beaufort scale",
      "admiral_sir_francis_beaufort_created_h": "Admiral Sir Francis Beaufort tsim nws lub wind scale xyoo 1805 raws li lub cua cuam tshuam rau cov nkoj kag. Beaufort scale niaj hnub siv cov ground observation: Force 0 (Calm) = pa taws sawv ncaj; Force 6 (Strong wind) = cov ceg loj ntsees, cov kaus vov tig; Force 12 (Hurricane) = kev puas tsuaj. Feem ntau cov noog nyiam tsiv nyob rau hauv cov cua Force 2-4 (cua me mus rau nrab).",
      "how_birds_use_wind": "🐦 Cov noog siv cua li cas",
      "tail_winds": "Tail winds: ",
      "migrants_strongly_prefer_flying_with_t": "Cov migrant nyiam heev ya nrog cua nyob rau tom qab. Ib qho tail wind tsuas yog 15 mph ua rau tus noog qhov ceev raws li av ob npaug nrog tib qhov kev siv zog. Cov kev tshawb fawb qhia tias nyob rau hnub tsiv uas muaj tail wind zoo, cov noog qhov txav mus los yog 10x ntau dua cov hnub headwind.",
      "dynamic_soaring": "Dynamic soaring: ",
      "albatrosses_exploit_wind_speed_gradien": "Albatrosses siv cov wind speed gradient saum cov nthwv dej hiav txwv. Los ntawm kev hloov nruab nrab kev nce mus rau cua ceev dua thiab dive mus rau cua qeeb dua ze npoo, lawv rho zog los ntawm wind shear nws tus kheej. Ib tug albatross tuaj yeem ya ntau txhiab mais yuav luag tsis ntxais tis.",
      "slope_soaring": "Slope soaring: ",
      "when_wind_hits_a_cliff_face_or_ridge_t": "Thaum cua ntaus ib lub cliff face los yog ridge, cov cua uas dov rov qab tsim ib lub «nthwv» lift raws li kab ridge. Cov raptor soar rau saum cov ridge current no thaum lub sijhawm tsiv, txuas cov roob zoo li dhia saum cov pob zeb. Hawk Mountain hauv Pennsylvania nto npe txog qhov tshwm sim no.",
      "experiment_place_a_thermal_and_a_mount": "Kev sim: tso ib lub thermal thiab ib lub roob rau hauv daim teb, ces ntxiv ib tug noog. Saib nws soar saum cov rising current!",
      "birds_as_weather_forecasters": "🌦️ Cov noog ua weather forecaster",
      "birds_are_exquisitely_sensitive_to_wea": "Cov noog rhiab heev rau cov hloov huab cua thiab tau siv ua «biological barometer» thoob keeb kwm:",
      "barometric_pressure": "Barometric pressure: ",
      "birds_can_detect_changes_in_barometric": "Cov noog tuaj yeem paub cov hloov ntawm barometric pressure ua tsaug rau cov receptor tshwj xeeb hauv middle ear (paratympanic organ). Thaum siab poob ua ntej ib qho cua daj cua dub, cov noog feem ntau ya qis dua thiab noj mov hnyav dua. Cov nqos ya qis yog ib qho storm precursor classic.",
      "some_birds_can_hear_infrasound_below_2": "Qee cov noog tuaj yeem hnov infrasound (qis dua 20 Hz) uas tsim los ntawm cov cua daj cua dub deb, cov nthwv dej hiav txwv, thiab txawm av qeeg. Golden-winged Warblers khiav tawm ntawm Tennessee 24 teev ua ntej ib qho tornado system tuaj txog xyoo 2014, raws li cov GPS transmitter ntes. Lawv ya ntau dua 900 mais los zam cov cua daj cua dub.",
      "cold_fronts": "Cold fronts: ",
      "autumn_migration_is_strongly_correlate": "Autumn migration muaj kev sib raug zoo nrog kev hla ntawm cov cold front. Cov noog soar saum cov cua northwest tom qab cov cold front, uas muab ob qho tail wind thiab lub ntuj tshiab. Cov birdwatcher muaj kev paub saib xyuas cov weather map los kwv yees cov hmo peak ntawm kev tsiv.",
      "fog_is_dangerous_for_migrating_birds_b": "Huab cua yog qhov txaus ntshai rau cov noog tsiv vim nws npog cov landmark thiab cov celestial navigation cue. Cov hmo fog uas muaj cloud base qis ua rau muaj «fallout», qhov chaw uas cov migrant nkees los ua pab rau hauv thawj lub chaw nyob uas muaj. Cov xwm txheej no, txawm tias txaus ntshai rau cov noog, tsim cov birdwatching opportunity zoo kawg.",
      "when_the_swallows_fly_high_the_weather": "«Thaum cov nqos ya siab, huab cua yuav qhuav. Thaum cov nqos ya qis, nag tuaj lawm.» — Cov lus paj lug no yeej tseeb raws li science: cov kab (cov nqos zaub mov) ya siab dua hauv cov high-pressure system thiab qis dua ua ntej cov cua daj cua dub.",
