      "early_spring_waterfowl_ducks_geese_hea": "Early spring: cov noog dej (os, os) mus rau sab qaum teb raws li kev yaj ntawm dej khov. Red-winged Blackbirds rov qab mus rau cov pas dej.",
      "peak_spring_warblers_vireos_tanagers_f": "Peak spring: cov warbler, vireo, thiab tanager puv sab qaum teb. Feem ntau cov songbird tsiv thaum hmo ntuj. Nyob rau hmo peak, muaj ntau dua 500 lab tus noog nyob saum huab cua.",
      "shorebirds_start_south_some_species_fa": "Cov shorebird pib mus sab qab teb — qee hom «swb» ntawm cov chaw yug thiab pib rov qab thaum ntxov Lub Xya Hli. Cov laus feem ntau ncaim ua ntej cov me nyuam.",
      "peak_fall_raptors_ride_thermals_along_": "Peak fall: cov raptor caij cov thermal raws li cov roob. Cov songbird raws cov cold front mus sab qab teb. Cov os ya hauv V formation thaum hmo ntuj.",
      "photoperiod_day_length_is_the_primary_": "Photoperiod (qhov ntev ntawm hnub) yog qhov trigger tseem ceeb ntawm kev tsiv. Thaum cov hnub luv dua thaum caij nplooj zeeg, cov hormone trigger «Zugunruhe» — kev tsis so ntawm kev tsiv — thiab cov noog pib khaws roj reserve (hyperphagia), qee zaus ntxiv lub cev qhov hnyav ob npaug.",
      "stopover_ecology": "⛺ Stopover ecology",
