      "refueling_stations": "cov refueling station",
      "critical_to_survival_a_migrating_warbl": " uas tseem ceeb rau kev ciaj sia. Ib tug warbler migrating yuav siv 75% ntawm lub sijhawm tsiv ntawm cov stopover, noj mov vwm los tsim roj reserve dua. Ib lub habitat stopover zoo yuav yog qhov txawv ntawm txoj sia thiab kev tuag.",
      "at_delaware_bay_over_1_million_shorebi": "Ntawm Delaware Bay, ntau dua 1 lab tus shorebird (Red Knots, Ruddy Turnstones, Sanderlings) vam khom rau cov qe horseshoe crab uas nteg thaum Lub Tsib Hlis. Lub sijhawm yuav tsum meej: cov noog tuaj txog raws nraim thaum cov horseshoe crab nteg qe. Yog cov horseshoe crab population poob (vim overfishing rau bait), tag nrho cov migration chain pob.",
      "conservation_success_story_after_horse": "Conservation success story: tom qab tsim cov horseshoe crab harvest limit xyoo 2012, cov Red Knot population pib rov qab qeeb qeeb los ntawm qhov qis tshaj critical 15,000 mus rau ntau dua 50,000 los ntawm 2025.",
      "migration_physiology": "🦴 Migration physiology",
