      "hyperphagia": "Hyperphagia",
      "before_migration_birds_enter_a_feeding": "Ua ntej tsiv, cov noog nkag mus rau kev noj mov vwm hu ua hyperphagia, noj mov ntawm tus nqi 2-3x ntawm ib txwm. Blackpoll Warbler (12 g) ntxiv 8-12 g ntawm roj reserve, yuav luag ua rau lub cev qhov hnyav ob npaug. Cov roj no yog fuel rau cov flight tsis nres ntau dua 2,000 mais.",
      "organ_shrinkage": "Organ shrinkage",
      "to_reduce_weight_migrating_birds_actua": "Los txo qhov hnyav, cov noog migrating tiag tiag shrink cov digestive organ (hnyuv, siab, gizzard) txog li 40% ua ntej ncaim. Thaum tuaj txog ntawm cov stopover, lawv rov tsim cov organ no sai los refuel. Qhov «phenotypic plasticity» no yog qhov tshwj xeeb hauv cov vertebrate.",
      "hemoglobin": "Hemoglobin",
      "high_altitude_migrants_like_bar_headed": "Cov high-altitude migrant, xws li Bar-headed Geese (uas ya saum Himalayas ntawm 29,000 ft), muaj hemoglobin tshwj xeeb nrog oxygen affinity siab dua. Lawv cov leeg muaj myoglobin ntxiv, thiab lawv qhov capillary density yog ob npaug ntawm cov lowland species.",
      "sleep_in_flight": "Pw tsaug zog thaum ya",
      "some_birds_can_sleep_while_flying_usin": "Qee cov noog tuaj yeem pw tsaug zog thaum ya, siv «hemispheric sleep» — kaw ib nrab ntawm lub hlwb ib zaug. Cov frigatebird raug sau tias pw 42 feeb ib hnub thaum lub sijhawm 10-hnub transoceanic flight, ua micro-sleep 12 seconds ib zaug.",
      "navigation_clock": "Navigation clock",
      "birds_maintain_an_internal_circadian_c": "Cov noog tuav ib lub internal circadian clock nrog qhov precision zoo kawg. Lub clock no compensate rau lub hnub qhov txav thoob ntuj (time-compensated sun compass) thiab taug qab cov seasonal change ntawm qhov ntev ntawm hnub uas trigger cov migration hormone.",
      "zugunruhe": "Zugunruhe",
      "zugunruhe_migration_restlessness_is_a_": "Zugunruhe («kev tsis so ntawm kev tsiv») yog ib qho behavioral state uas cov noog migratory uas raug kaw hauv lub tawb flutter mus rau qhov kev taw uas lawv yuav tsiv raws li ntuj, nyob rau lub sijhawm uas lawv yuav tsiv. Nws tau tsav los ntawm hormone thiab coded genetically. Txawm cov noog uas tau tu los ntawm tes, tsis muaj migration experience, tseem qhia Zugunruhe.",
