      "bird_banding": "Bird banding: ",
      "since_1920_over_80_million_birds_have_": "Txij li xyoo 1920, ntau dua 80 lab tus noog tau raug band hauv North America. Txhua lub band muaj ib tus lej tshwj xeeb. Thaum ib tug banded bird raug ntes dua, cov scientist kawm txog kev ciaj sia, txoj kev, thiab lub sijhawm. Cov recovery rate qis (1-5%), tab sis cov dataset loj heev.",
      "gps_trackers": "GPS trackers: ",
      "solar_powered_gps_tags_now_as_small_as": "Cov solar-powered GPS tag (tam sim no me li 1 g) xa cov location data los ntawm satellite. Lawv qhia cov txoj kev raug, cov stopover time, thiab cov flight altitude. Godwit qhov 7,145-mile non-stop flight raug track nrog GPS.",
      "light_level_geolocators_0_5g_record_su": "Cov light-level geolocator (0.5 g) sau cov sunrise thiab sunset time. Thaum ib tug noog raug ntes dua, cov scientist rho cov data thiab suav latitude (los ntawm qhov ntev ntawm hnub) thiab longitude (los ntawm solar noon time). Precision: ~200 km.",
      "weather_radar": "Weather radar: ",
      "nexrad_weather_radar_stations_across_t": "Cov NEXRAD weather radar station thoob US ntes cov pab noog migratory loj. BirdCast (Cornell Lab) siv machine learning los kwv yees thiab visualize kev tsiv real-time los ntawm cov radar data. Nyob rau cov hmo peak, radar qhia cov green blotch loj ntawm bird migration.",
      "citizen_scientists_submit_100_million_": "Cov citizen scientist xa ntau dua 100 lab tus bird observation ib xyoos los ntawm eBird, tsim lub biodiversity database loj tshaj plaws hauv ntiaj teb. Cov data no qhia cov continental-scale migration timing thiab distribution pattern uas tsis muaj research team tuaj yeem khaws lawv ib leeg.",
