      "dreaming_stage_brain_is_highly_active_": "Theem npau suav. Lub hlwb ua haujlwm heev (zoo li kev tsim dheev), tab sis lub cev tuag tes tuag taw (atonia vim brainstem txwv cov motor neurons). Qhov muag txav sai ua ke. Kev ua cov nco emotional thiab kev daws teeb meem tsim. Cov cycles ntev dua thoob hmo.",
