      "a_scale_is_an_ordered_set_of_pitches_m": "Ib qho scale yog ib pawg pitches uas muaj kev txiav. Cov modes yog cov rotations ntawm scale uas pib ntawm cov degrees sib txawv. Txhua qho tsim ib qho mood txawv.",
      "chords_are_built_by_stacking_intervals": "Cov chords raug tsim los ntawm kev tsub cov intervals (3rds). Major siv ib qho major 3rd + minor 3rd. Minor rov qab lawv. Extended chords ntxiv 7ths, 9ths, thiab ntau dua.",
      "kicks_use_a_sine_oscillator_with_a_pit": "Cov kicks siv ib qho sine oscillator nrog pitch sweep. Cov snares sib xyaw noise (filtered) + tone body. Cov hi-hats siv high-pass filtered noise bursts.",
      "4_4_4_quarter_note_beats_per_bar_most_": "4/4 = 4 quarter-note beats hauv ib bar (feem ntau tshaj). 3/4 = waltz feel. 6/8 = compound duple. 5/4 thiab 7/8 tsim cov grooves asymmetric, txawv.",
