      "every_musical_sound_contains_overtones": "Txhua lub suab nkauj muaj overtones saum lub fundamental. Lawv lub zog sib piv txiav txim rau timbre — vim li cas trumpet thiaj nrov txawv ntawm flute ntawm tib lub pitch.",
      "an_interval_is_the_distance_between_tw": "Ib qho interval yog qhov deb ntawm ob pitches, ntsuas hauv semitones. Frequency ratio txiav txim rau consonance (cov ratios yooj yim li 3:2 nrov du).",
