      "opportunity_rover_found_hematite_blueb": "Lub rover Opportunity nrhiav tau cov hematite \"blueberries\" — cov pob zeb uas tsuas tsim tau hauv dej xwb. Cov duab los saum ntuj qhia cov delta dej qub!",
      "venus_is_hotter_462_c_vs_430_c_mercury": "Venus kub dua (462°C vs 430°C)! Mercury tsis muaj huab cua los kaw cov kub. Greenhouse effect tseem ceeb dua kev deb.",
      "gas_giants_have_no_solid_surface_they_": "Cov gas giant tsis muaj saum npoo tawv! Lawv feem ntau yog pa hydrogen thiab helium uas nyhav zuj zus mus rau lub plawv. Ib lub probe yuav tog mus tsis kawg.",
      "earth_s_distance_from_the_sun_doesn_t_": "Ntiaj Teb qhov deb ntawm Lub Hnub tsis hloov thaum nruab hnub. Tav su tsuas txhais tias Lub Hnub siab tshaj hauv koj lub ntuj. Ntiaj Teb ze tshaj rau lub Ib Hlis (perihelion)!",
      "jupiter_is_11x_wider_than_earth_and_1_": "Jupiter dav 11 npaug dua Ntiaj Teb, thiab 1,300 lub Ntiaj Teb yuav nkag tau hauv nws! Lub solar system muaj qhov loj me sib txawv heev.",
      "pluto_is_still_in_the_solar_system_it_": "Pluto tseem nyob hauv solar system! Nws raug hloov npe los ntawm \"planet\" ua \"dwarf planet\" xyoo 2006, tab sis nws tseem ncig Lub Hnub.",
      "the_asteroid_belt_is_mostly_empty_spac": "Lub siv asteroid feem ntau yog chaw khoob! Qhov deb nruab nrab cov asteroid yog ntau lab km. Cov nkoj ntuj ya hla yam tsis muaj kev txaus ntshai.",
      "not_always_saturn_is_95x_earth_s_mass_": "Tsis yog txhua zaus! Saturn hnyav 95 npaug dua Ntiaj Teb tab sis lub zog rub saum npoo tsuas yog 1.06g vim nws loj heev thiab tsis nyhav. Qhov hnyav nyob ntawm ob yam — qhov hnyav THIAB qhov dav.",
      "all_parts_of_the_moon_receive_sunlight": "Txhua sab ntawm Lub Hli tau txais qhov ci ntawm Lub Hnub! Sab \"nraum qab\" tsuas yog ib nrab uas peb saib tsis pom los ntawm Ntiaj Teb vim tidal locking. Nws tau Lub Hnub ib yam nkaus.",
      "the_habitable_zone": "Thaj Chaw Nyob Tau",
      "the_habitable_zone_or_goldilocks_zone_": "Thaj chaw nyob tau (los sis \"Goldilocks zone\") yog cov kev deb ntawm ib lub hnub qub uas dej kua nyob tau saum ib lub planet. Hauv peb lub solar system, Venus nyob ntawm ntug sab hauv, Ntiaj Teb nyob nruab nrab, thiab Mars nyob ntawm ntug sab nraud. Tab sis yuav muaj dej kua tseem yuav tsum muaj huab cua thiab lub zog magnetic zoo thiab!",
      "the_greenhouse_effect": "Qhov Greenhouse Effect",
      "when_sunlight_heats_a_planet_s_surface": "Thaum qhov ci ntawm Lub Hnub ua kub ib lub planet saum npoo, saum npoo tso cov kub rov tawm (infrared). Cov pa greenhouse (CO₂, CH₄, H₂O) nqus cov kub no thiab tso rov qab, ua rau lub planet sov. Ntiaj Teb qhov greenhouse yog +33°C (txhawb txoj sia). Venus qhov yog +510°C (tswj tsis tau). Mars yuav luag tsis muaj li (nruab nrab -60°C). Cov pa greenhouse muaj ntau npaum li cas txiav txim qhov tshwm sim!",
      "magnetic_shields": "Cov Daim Thaiv Magnetic",
      "a_planet_s_magnetic_field_creates_a_ma": "Ib lub planet lub zog magnetic tsim ib qho \"magnetosphere\" — ib daim thaiv pom tsis tau uas thawb cua ntawm Lub Hnub (cov hmoov hluav taws xob los ntawm Lub Hnub). Ntiaj Teb lub magnetosphere tiv thaiv peb cov huab cua thiab ua rau txoj sia muaj tau. Mars poob nws lub zog magnetic 4 txhiab lab xyoo dhau los, thiab nws cov huab cua raug nplawm ploj zuj zus. Jupiter lub magnetosphere muaj zog 20,000 npaug dua Ntiaj Teb qhov!",
      "why_isn_t_pluto_a_planet": "Vim Li Cas Pluto Tsis Yog Ib Lub Planet?",
      "in_2006_the_international_astronomical": "Xyoo 2006, International Astronomical Union txhais peb yam rau ib lub planet: (1) Ncig Lub Hnub ✓, (2) Muaj qhov hnyav txaus kom zoo li lub pob kheej kheej ✓, (3) Tau \"ntxuav nws txoj kev ncig\" kom tsis muaj lwm cov khib nyiab ✗. Pluto sib koom nws thaj kev ncig nrog ntau txhiab lub cev Kuiper Belt, yog li nws raug faib ua ib lub \"dwarf planet.\" Qhov no tsis ua rau nws tsis txaus nyiam — New Horizons qhia tias nws tseem txav thiab hloov!",
      "tidal_locking": "Kev Sib Khi (Tidal Locking)",
      "over_billions_of_years_gravitational_t": "Tau ntau txhiab lab xyoo, lub zog rub ntawm tides ua rau ib lub hli tig qeeb zuj zus mus txog thaum nws tig raws nraim li nws lub sij hawm ncig. Qhov tshwm sim: ib sab ntsia rau lub planet tas mus li. Peb Lub Hli khi rau Ntiaj Teb li ntawd. Mercury khi ib nrab rau Lub Hnub (piv 3:2). Pluto thiab Charon sib khi — ob lub qhia tib sab rau ib leeg tas mus li!",
      "searching_for_life": "Tab tom nrhiav txoj sia",
      "a_biosignature_is_any_evidence_of_past": "Ib qho biosignature yog ib yam pov thawj ntawm txoj sia yav tas los sis tam sim no. Cov kws tshawb fawb nrhiav: (1) dej kua, (2) cov organic molecule, (3) cov pa hauv huab cua li oxygen los sis methane uas yuav tsis muaj yog tsis muaj txoj sia tsim lawv, (4) cov chaw muab lub zog. Cov chaw zoo tshaj hauv peb lub solar system: Mars (dej qub), Europa (dej hiav txwv hauv qab), Enceladus (cov geyser dej), thiab Titan (cov pas dej methane).",
